Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Hello Venus talk about having hoobaes for 'Dazed and Confused' By jennywill 6 minutes ago 860 62 1 0 Google+ Hello Venus talked about their 6-year-long career with ' Dazed and Confused '.
The girls had a photoshoot with the fashion magazine, and they were asked how they felt about reaching their 6th year since debut. The girls said, " We still feel like rookies, so we don't know how to act when hoobaes greet us at music shows. We think that since we have so many hoobaes now, we should be more responsible. Each year is different. We learn something new every day. " 
On the most 'mysterious' member, the girls picked Yeoreum , explaining, " Yeoreum is impossible to predict. Her name isn't Yeoreum for no reason, and she has an unstoppable passion and energy. She gives life to the group. "Are you surprised by the members' pick for most mysterious member? YOU MAY LIKE GET AKP IN YOUR INBOX! ..or follow allkpop to stay updated: Tags:
